description	"Kyle Katarn

Class: Jedi.
Class Summary:
A Jedi/gunner hybrid that rewards flanking, skirmishing, and swapping between weapons and force powers. 

Lightsaber:
- Defense (2)
- Deflect (2)
- Can use Yellow and Red styles

Weapons:
- Lightsaber
- Bryar Pistol (3)
- Concussion Grenades (2)
- Trip Mine (1)

Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Push (2)
- Pull (3)
- Sense (2)
- Protect (2)
- Grip (2)
- Force Block (2)
- Force Focus (1)
- Improved Saberthrow

Attributes:
- BP Free Jumps

After learning of Morgan Katarn's death at the hands of Jerec, Kyle Katarn chose to continue his murdered father's mission of protecting the Valley of the Jedi's immense power from being abused. In the process of fighting through Jerec's minions, Kyle managed to teach himself about the Force and the ways of the Jedi."